The media project worker.


Subprocesses:

- download.py:
    unpack, clean and sort downloaded media

- extra.py:
    fetch and update local files metadata

- file.py:
    manage local files

- media_finder.py:
    find new media from the files metadata (movies directors, music similar bands), and add new searches

- release.py:
    fetch new releases from the web (vcdquality releases, tvrage schedule, sputnikmusic reviews), and add new searches for validated releases

- search.py:
    process and manage the searches, add new searches when required (e.g.: tv episodes)

- subtitles.py:
    fetch and manage subtitles for video files

- transmission.py:
    manage transmission downloads


Start the worker:
./mediaworker/run.py
